{
  "stem": "27390.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "But it was impossible to live there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "You see, thousands and thousands of people came from different-- from the territory that was occupied by the-- was-- was annexed into Germany.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "So being a little town, we-- there was not enough to eat.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And there was no room there to sleep.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "My-- my uncle didn't have room for us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And then we had, you see-- and the Germans, I didn't know that then.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "But from what I've read, what went on, the Germans wanted to get rid of the Jews from the Reich to start with.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "But there was the governor of the protectorate, his name, I've read it in a book somewhere.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "His name was Frank.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "You might have heard of him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And he-- maybe a lot of Poles also were driven out, not just Jews.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So there were a few million people in that area.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he couldn't cope with all these people.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was frightened there would be a riot.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There would be an uprising.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So he protested the whole time to Germany, to Berlin, that this can't go on.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So they had to look for different ways what to do with the Jews.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So then we had-- but we didn't know all this was going on.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I only read this after the war.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But at the time, we heard that Lodz was quieting down, and they're not driving out any more Jews.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So my father-- and we had-- there we had nothing to eat in this [INAUDIBLE] we-- we-- no-- no more food.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Everything was very expensive.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We used up practically all the money we had to buy food.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
